OL,3,CReview to probe potential failures to
OL,4,Cmanage risk over showjumper murder
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FA review is to be commissioned to
OL,8,Festablish whether opportunities were
OL,9,Fmissed to handle the risks presented
OL,10,Fby the man accused of the murder of
OL,11,Fshowjumper Katie Simpson.
OL,13,FThe trial of Jonathan Creswell, 36,
OL,14,Ffor the murder of Ms Simpson, ended in
OL,15,FApril last year after his sudden death.
OL,17,FThe showjumper, 21, from Tynan, Co
OL,18,FArmagh, died in Altnagelvin hospital
OL,19,Falmost a week after an incident in
OL,20,FGortnessy Meadows, Lettershandoney, in
OL,21,FCo Londonderry, on August 3 2020.
