OL,7,FPolice originally thought she had
OL,8,Ftaken her own life.
OL,10,FIt was not until the following year
OL,11,Fthat Creswell, the partner of Ms
OL,12,FSimpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,15,FCreswell had previously been jailed
OL,16,Fafter being convicted of assaulting a
OL,17,Fformer partner in 2009.
OL,19,FIt has emerged that Creswell was not
OL,20,Fsubject to a risk management plan at
OL,21,Fthe time of Ms Simpson's death.
