OL,4,Cmanage risk over showjumper murder
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FJustice minister Naomi Long has now
OL,8,Fcommissioned a review to establish
OL,9,Fwhether opportunities were missed to
OL,10,Frefer Creswell into the Public
OL,11,FProtection Arrangements Northern
OL,12,FIreland (PPANI).
OL,14,FMs Long's Alliance Party colleague and
OL,15,FPolicing Board member Nuala
OL,16,FMcAllister, had asked the minister if
OL,17,Fshe would commission a Serious Case
OL,18,FReview (SCR) under the terms of the
OL,19,FPPANI to consider whether there had
OL,20,Fbeen potential referral failures in
OL,21,Fthe case of Creswell.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
