OL,7,FIn a written answer, the minister said
OL,8,Fa SCR was only applicable for cases
OL,9,Falready managed through PPANI.
OL,11,FAs Creswell was not being managed
OL,12,Funder the arrangements, Ms Long said a
OL,13,FSerious Case Review would be
OL,14,F"speculative" and beyond scope.
