OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,FHowever, the minister said she was
OL,8,Fcommitted to a separate review of the
OL,9,FCreswell case to examine if there had
OL,10,Fbeen opportunities to refer him into
OL,11,Fthe risk management arrangements. She
OL,12,Fhas also instigated a general review
OL,13,Fof the referral process.
OL,15,FMs Long said she recognised that there
OL,16,F"may have been points at which
OL,17,FJonathan Creswell could have been
OL,18,Freferred into PPANI for management
OL,19,Funder those arrangements".
