OL,4,Cmanage risk over showjumper murder
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,F"It is vital that we fully understand
OL,8,Fthe circumstances and take account of
OL,9,Fany learning around the management of
OL,10,Fserious offenders," she added.
OL,12,F"I have therefore commissioned the
OL,13,Findependent Lay Advisers, who are
OL,14,Fappointed by statute to oversee and
OL,15,Fmonitor PPANI, to review the general
OL,16,Frobustness and operation of the
OL,17,Freferral process.
OL,19,F"I am also committed to a specific
OL,20,Freview of the Creswell case.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@SO]tD@AOU{D@AOU
