OL,3,CReview to probe potential failures to
OL,4,Cmanage risk over showjumper murder
OL,5,Caccused
OL,7,F"This review is intended to establish
OL,8,Fwhen he came into contact with any of
OL,9,Fthe PPANI agencies; if there were
OL,10,Fopportunities to refer him into the
OL,11,Farrangements; and to identify learning.
OL,13,F"The review will also consider those
OL,14,Fpoints which have been raised in
OL,15,Fcorrespondence to my department and to
OL,16,Fthe PPANI co-ordinator.
OL,18,F"The full terms of reference are being
OL,19,Ffinalised and it is my intention to
OL,20,Fappoint an independent reviewer to
OL,21,Fundertake this work."
