OL,7,FMs McAllister welcomed the minister's
OL,8,Fundertaking.
OL,10,F"I have been consistently clear the
OL,11,Fserious failings in relation to
OL,12,FJonathan Creswell must be uncovered
OL,13,Fand so I welcome this confirmation
OL,14,Ffrom the Justice Minister," she said.
OL,16,F"I am glad the urgent need to review
OL,17,Fpotential failures was taken seriously.
OL,19,F"Creswell had a violent history and a
OL,20,Fcriminal record which reflected this."
