OL,7,FMs McAllister said there was evidence
OL,8,Fthat indicated that opportunities were
OL,9,Fmissed by the PSNI and that PPANI
OL,10,Farrangements should have been in place
OL,11,Fto manage Creswell.
OL,13,FIn regard to the investigation into Ms
OL,14,FSimpson's death, police in Northern
OL,15,FIreland have apologised to her family
OL,16,Fafter a watchdog found their initial
OL,17,Fprobe was flawed.
